2022).\n  We finally show that the $q$-ary count-free pebble game is unable to\ndistinguish even Abelian groups. This extends the result of Grochow & Levet\n(arXiv 2022), who established the result in the case of $q = 1$. The general\ntheme is that some counting appears necessary to place \\textsc{Group\nIsomorphism} into $\\textsf{P}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2022 18:19:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-22"}
