o calculate the\nChern-Simons currents for both gravitational and electromagnetic chiral\nanomalies in the black hole spacetime, and discuss the properties of the\nchirality fluxes associated with these currents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2022 19:33:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2023 00:50:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-08"}
