oach uses GIPSL\nspecifications as a starting point to derive ILP problem generators for a\nspecific application domain automatically. First experiments show that the\nderived ILP problem generators can compete with hand-crafted programs developed\nby ILP experts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2022 11:52:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-23"}
